Q: What is 60% of 30% of 1400 grams?
Options: (a) 450 gms (b) 100 gms (c) 252 gms (d) 240 gms (e) None of these
A:
30% of 1400 grams = 420 grams. 60% of 420 grams = 252 grams. So the answer is (c).

